{
  "stem": "8892.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "She doesn't even know who the husband is, and so forth and so on-- her life story.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And she actually pitied us, and felt sorry.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "My 16th birthday in December 10, is in there in Grunberg.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And my sister saves her ration of bread to give it to me next morning-- my birthday present.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And I must have been the youngest in the whole group, I think.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Because there was very few 14 and 15-year-olds left.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And so they knew it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And I think my cousin, Magda, and all of them, they give me extra margarine or something.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "So I had a little packet under my pillow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And as I-- you know, when we get up, the first thing you have to make the bunk.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Straighten the bunk before you get off.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And you had a certain amount of time for that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And I'd make the bed and I see warm socks in there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And we knew, because she was that night in the barrack with us, the young girl, the German, who was actually nice and decent and kind.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "She never hit nobody-- nobody was ever by punished by her.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And I looked at her, and I smiled.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And I thank her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Danke, danke.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And I knew it was her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And sure enough, I put the warm socks on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "So I had to run, drag layer-- I had to throw off and it was better.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And that was my 16th birthday there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "So we were there until January.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After Grunberg, they emptying again, we're hearing a bombing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I have to tell you that factory was so camouflaged, so geniusly, that until you got to that factory door, you didn't see it's a building there.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The evergreens, the greens, just like you see them in a movie, even better.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
